### 2.6 Update Homepage & Navigation
- Add all 5 new tools to the tools grid on `index.html`
- Update footer links to include new tools
- Update `sitemap.xml`:
  - Add 5 new tool URLs
  - Priority: 0.8
  - lastmod: 2026-05-12
  - changefreq: monthly
- Add breadcrumb schema for navigation

